---
title: Mexican Pulled Beef Bowl with Charred Corn Salsa & Cheesy Tortillas Chips
description: Gather round for another sensational night of pulled meats! On today’s menu; pulled beef cooked up in a richly spiced sauce and paired with homemade cheesy nacho chips ready to satisfy all your crunchin’ needs. Dig in and enjoy the show of flavours.

*Our pulled beef is gently cooked while vacuum-sealed (or sous vide as the French say). The meat may look pale, but it's packed with flavour and moisture!*
